channel.title: Fun-scape 712 Rsps - Need Staff - Drop Party at 20 players
channel.description:
Hey guys. Fun-scape is a fairly new rsps, we need players and staff so join today. It is a 712 with all working bosses and donator zone. We also have glacors and there will be a dp at 20+ players. It is an eco server with great shops.
Cmds: ::train ::shops ::Home ::dzone ::sz (staff only)
The link to the video is : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e3kaevrttui&feature=youtu.be
The download link is in the video! Enjoy
